== Lists

=== Unordered

- Parser and AST
- Formatter and LSP
- HTML and PDF renderers
- EPUB 3 renderer (new in Phase 12)

=== Ordered

1. Parse the source document
2. Resolve includes and variables
3. Render to target format
4. Validate output

=== Definition List

EPUB : Electronic Publication format based on XHTML and CSS

MathML : Mathematical Markup Language for rendering equations in browsers and EPUB

SVG : Scalable Vector Graphics for diagrams and charts

